ygData.messageBody:
Drmom are you on any instant mess if so let me know so i can add ya... hehe you replied to this right after i wrote it.  I have a level 57 warrioress on Xegony that i dont play at all... i have a few other mediocre characters on Atonious bayle and Firona Vie... im not too concerned about gear, just some fellow sisterhood.. so any server is good for me..if you have room on Quellios for another character that would be fine with me.

"Dr. Mom" <drmom5@...> wrote:
OK decide server;  /random 1 16.
Giggle.

I think the server where the woman who has the highest level
character or guild to help us out, should be the one.
Alternatively, who has the time to set up a new guild and list it
on ezboard? 

I have a great guild with many high ranking older women in it.
(read, Aego casters.)

I have a level 50 wiz on Quellious.  I don't want to move her
because of my wonderful guild.

Someone come up with a clever last name and guild name.  We can do
a poll on Yahoo.  Women of Power?
